{"id": 3070, "genre": 1001, "title": "你在人际关系中都见到/经历过哪些微妙的“小型暴力”？", "description": "就和“暴力式沟通”一样，社交中啥样的举动会让你想把它分到”隐形暴力”那一挂？（题图来自：iStock ©️ CSA-Archive）", "record_count": 1303, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20191126004319HB0JIlONzZ5gimxA.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-11-25T17:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 349981, "content": "只想低调得减个肥，身边的同事/亲戚大声得说“就吃这么点，你不会是在减肥吧”，引得其他人也开始关注你我了什么，吃了多少", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1534398}, {"id": 349757, "content": "情侣之间的各种“求生欲测试”", "image": null, "praise_count": 137, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 349758, "content": "社交平台的“账号被博主拉黑删评后，会被全平台禁评x天”功能", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 349759, "content": "工作群中的“@所有人，收到xx分钟内回复”", "image": null, "praise_count": 188, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 349761, "content": "日常中习惯性用“吃瓜”来概括任何一个人的新闻", "image": null, "praise_count": 61, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 349762, "content": "喜欢说“你听懂了吗？”而不是礼貌的“我说清楚了吗？”的同级同事。", "image": null, "praise_count": 276, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 986294}, {"id": 349764, "content": "别人的沾沾自喜摇摆头看你后，对着你说了一句“蠢”", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1478569}, {"id": 349765, "content": "被说皮肤黑。", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1612661}, {"id": 349766, "content": "“帮帮忙 好伐”", "image": null, "praise_count": 63, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 651076}, {"id": 349767, "content": "午餐时间，瘦子同事说吃不下最近又胖了", "image": null, "praise_count": 36, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1672353}, {"id": 349768, "content": "针对你的外貌或性格缺陷指指点点，明明只是比你早进公司几天，就开始教导你做事", "image": null, "praise_count": 98, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1664029}, {"id": 349770, "content": "买东西的时候商家的各种冷嘲热讽，不就是没买你家东西吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 391490}, {"id": 349771, "content": "等等，你先听我说。", "image": null, "praise_count": 59, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1652793}, {"id": 349772, "content": "聊不到几句就想八你的隐私，对不起我不需要一个调查户口的同事", "image": null, "praise_count": 59, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 671570}, {"id": 349774, "content": "学自己讲话", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1664314}, {"id": 349775, "content": "“以后写完本子先给我看，别交给xx（更高一级）”\n此甩手掌柜让我直接与更高一级沟通，等我真的越级沟通了，她又幽幽地出现了，话里话外带着对我未通过“测试”的失望。", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1672381}, {"id": 349776, "content": "忽略对方明显的暗示，假装不经意却对别人避而不谈的事情刨根问底", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1647656}, {"id": 349777, "content": "发来一个分享助力链接", "image": null, "praise_count": 41, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1285008}, {"id": 349778, "content": "迎新聚餐\\聚会", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1531372}, {"id": 349779, "content": "午饭桌上，我正和一个同事聊着事情，话还没说完，旁边另一位同事直接开启话匣子，脸朝着我说事的同事，眼睛盯着我…丝毫不会觉得尴尬地继续说他的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1427644}, {"id": 349780, "content": "朋友对我说：我说这些是为了你好 你不要说你的感受 就算我懂你的感受给带给我多少钱还是怎么样。感觉心好凉 谢谢你对我好和建议 我也知道我的感受不重要 总有一天你会知道感受有多重要", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1672400}, {"id": 349781, "content": "被网易小暴力辞退 蹭你热度", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1460269}, {"id": 349782, "content": "“哦。”", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1437096}, {"id": 349783, "content": "我总是吃不胖，不长肉，不吸收啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1188058}, {"id": 349784, "content": "一有任务，搭档就不回复消息，以至于自己分担了大部分工作。", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1670859}, {"id": 349786, "content": "不回话。", "image": null, "praise_count": 50, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1627500}, {"id": 349790, "content": "帮下忙嘛，反正你也没什么事情干", "image": null, "praise_count": 28, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1672437}, {"id": 350046, "content": "打断别人说话", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1200442}, {"id": 349791, "content": "我是那个冷暴力的家伙，其实我是以暴制暴", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 665111}, {"id": 349793, "content": "采用冷暴力逼你辞职", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1165895}, {"id": 349796, "content": "你也这样觉得吧！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1511959}, {"id": 349797, "content": "做完赶快下班吧🙄", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 918774}, {"id": 350055, "content": "你把xxxxxxxxx，你这样可是要扣绩效的哦", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1673591}, {"id": 349826, "content": "上司问我：对吧，我说的是不是这个道理，是的话点头", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1428866}, {"id": 349848, "content": "故意和你不喜欢的人走在一起", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1672819}, {"id": 349879, "content": "我说话的时候总说得了得了 就像我很吧唧一样", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1578854}, {"id": 349881, "content": "扯到国族主义的时候。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1492840}, {"id": 349882, "content": "上级的所有双标要求！", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1045935}, {"id": 349888, "content": "模仿他人，打断谈话，不经同意加入组局", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1672908}, {"id": 349891, "content": "本来气氛好好的，你一开口大家刻意的沉默", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1672971}, {"id": 349903, "content": "每天说着自己怎么怎么忙，然后对你说看你好像一直没什么事做。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1335123}, {"id": 349904, "content": "因为大龄单身女性而经常被亲密的同事开一些略略擦边球的玩笑", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1672761}, {"id": 349905, "content": "“你有必要吗？”", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1575616}, {"id": 350936, "content": "你做梦", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1662296}, {"id": 349913, "content": "领导莫名其妙对你态度奇差也得默默忍着", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1216775}, {"id": 349918, "content": "。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1605759}, {"id": 349933, "content": "我就说两句(结果说了半个小时多)", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1673223}]}